{
  "message": "fuzz(fj-conformance): add 23 structured corpus seeds for primitive_eval_fuzzer\n\nAdds targeted seeds covering control flow and special function primitives:\n- Cond: true/false paths, zero values\n- Switch: index 0/1 selection\n- Scan: init values with sum operation\n- While: count up, immediate exit conditions\n- Lgamma/Digamma: boundary values (1, 0.5, 2, large)\n- ErfInv: zero and 0.5\n- Cbrt: negative, zero, positive values\n- Copy, BitcastConvertType, ReducePrecision edge cases\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
